Opt1 — User-Facing Distribution Terms
=====================================

Copyright (c) 2026 Jacob Healey.

Opt1 is a free, non-commercial fan tool for *RuneScape*. It is provided
free of charge for personal use. There is no paid tier, no donation-required
feature, no advertising, and no input automation.

You are free to:

  - Download, install, and run Opt1 on your own computer for personal use.
  - Share unmodified copies of the released binary with other players, as
    long as you also share the accompanying `LICENSES/THIRD_PARTY_LICENSES.md`
    file (or an equivalent notice) so downstream users see the third-party
    attributions and licences.

You may NOT:

  - Redistribute Opt1 commercially (charging for it, bundling it into a
    paid product, or making it part of an ad-supported service). This
    restriction is required to keep the bundled RuneScape Wiki assets
    compliant with their Creative Commons NonCommercial clause.
  - Strip or replace the in-app *Credits & Licenses* screen, or the bundled
    third-party licence notices, when redistributing the binary.
  - Use the name "Opt1" or this logo to imply endorsement by Jagex Ltd.,
    the RuneScape Wiki, or the upstream ClueTrainer project.

